First, audit where your employees spend hours on manual, repetitive tasks. Is it copying bank transfer receipts from email into your accounting systems? Is it manually assigning customer leads from Facebook ads to sales agents in Lekki?

Second, write clean integrations for those specific pathways. Build a solid foundation with webhooks, and then layer on lightweight AI models for automated triage. When you run things this way, your business gains immediate margin improvements.

